#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wine_merchant.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade your Wine Shop package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"¿No has importado los datos de demostración? Todavía puedes hacerlo. "
"Dirígete a Aplicaciones &gt; Sectores &gt; Actualiza el paquete para "
"vinotecas y selecciona la casilla correspondiente."

#. module: wine_merchant
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wine_merchant.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You recently did a tour of the vineyards in France or in Italy and you wish "
"to keep a trace of your recent purchases? Record them in the<strong> "
"purchase app</strong>"
msgstr ""
"¿Ha realizado recientemente un tour por los viñedos de Francia o Italia y "
"desea conservar un registro de sus últimas compras? Regístrelas en la "
"<strong>aplicación Compras</strong>."

#. module: wine_merchant
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wine_merchant.welcome_article_body
